oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The A.F.A. Convention this past Augustat the Queen Mary had a new featureadded to it , The AVY AWARD. Severalmonths ago Lee Horton, Jean Hessler,and I were busy putting together thisyear's convention and in the process o(time we came up with the idea of anaward for individual achievement inavicul ture. While tossing the idea aroundseveral things came up , the award shouldbe for everyone, all clubs should beinvolved. It was decided that we neededcategories, nominations would have tocome from the member clubs and, ifcourse, a name had to be found.
